---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Flu Symptoms &amp; Treatment in Dallas–Fort Worth | AymanCare"
  description="Fever, cough, body aches? Get same-day flu testing and treatment at AymanCare. Four DFW clinics, walk-ins welcome."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Services\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Flu Symptoms\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/flu-treatment/\"}]}"} />
  </Fragment>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="breadcrumbs fade-in">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">✦</span><a href="/services/">Services</a><span class="sep">✦</span><span>Flu Symptoms</span>
  </div>

  <div class="svc-hero">
    <div>
      <span class="svc-hero-badge fade-in"><span class="ic"></span>Rapid testing available</span>
      <h1 class="page-title fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">Flu <em>symptoms</em> &<br>treatment.</h1>
      <p class="svc-hero-lede fade-in">Board-certified diagnosis and treatment for influenza and flu-like illness — so you can get the right care, feel better faster, and protect the people around you.</p>
      <div class="svc-hero-chips fade-in"><span class="pill">Rapid testing</span><span class="pill pill-accent">Same-day care</span><span class="pill">All ages</span></div>
      <div class="svc-hero-ctas fade-in">
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book this visit →</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-hero-visual fade-in">
      <img src="/images/flu-care.jpg" alt="Flu Symptoms">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <aside class="svc-aside">
      <div class="aside-card fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Service details</div>
        <h3>Symptoms we <em>treat</em></h3>
        <ul><li>Fever, chills, body aches</li><li>Sore throat & cough</li><li>Fatigue & congestion</li><li>Nausea & vomiting</li><li>Headaches & sinus pressure</li><li>Respiratory symptoms</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-card dark fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Ready to book?</div>
        <h3>Same-day <em>appointments</em> available.</h3>
        <a href="/contact/" class="big-num">View all locations →</a>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Call or book online — walk-ins welcome at every location.</p>
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-accent" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Book online →</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="svc-content">
      <h2>More than <em>just a cold.</em></h2><p>Influenza is a contagious respiratory illness caused by flu viruses — and it can knock out even healthy adults for a week or more. At AymanCare, our board-certified physicians work closely with nurse practitioners to diagnose and treat the flu quickly and thoroughly.</p><h2><em>Rapid testing</em> & diagnosis.</h2><p>We offer rapid flu testing with results in as little as 15 minutes. For many patients, same-visit diagnosis means same-visit treatment — including antivirals like Tamiflu when appropriate and clinically indicated.</p><blockquote>"The flu isn't just an inconvenience. For the right patients, early diagnosis and treatment can change the course of the whole illness."</blockquote><h2>Recovery <em>support.</em></h2><p>Beyond medication, we help you plan: what to eat, when to call us if things worsen, and how to protect your family while you recover. For high-risk patients — young children, seniors, pregnancy, or compromised immune systems — we follow up closely.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-grid-band">
  <div class="svc-grid-band-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ At a glance</span>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">By the <em>numbers.</em></h2>
    <div class="three-col"><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">< 15min</div>
      <h4>Rapid test results</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">Same-day</div>
      <h4>Treatment</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">All ages</div>
      <h4>Adult & pediatric</h4>
    </div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
<section class="related-services">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: none;">
        <div>
          <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ Related services</span>
          <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">Explore <em>more</em>.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="related-grid"><a href="/services/primary-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Primary</em> Care</h4>
          <p>Long-term care and annual wellness — your family physician.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/walk-in-urgent-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Walk-In</em> Urgent</h4>
          <p>Same-day care for acute illness, injury, and COVID testing.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/pediatric-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Pediatric</em> Care</h4>
          <p>Child-centered care from newborn to teen.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a></div>
    </section>
</section>

<section class="big-cta">
  <div class="big-cta-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in">◆ Ready when you are</span>
    <h2 class="fade-in">Let's take care<br>of <em>you.</em></h2>
    <p class="fade-in">Book online in under a minute, or walk into any of our four Dallas-area locations today.</p>
    <div class="cta-row fade-in">
      <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book appointment →</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
